&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage prospects and identify clients to contact via phone, e-mail, Linkedin, and other creative channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the sales team and educate them on details of opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage expectations and overcome objections.&lt;/li&gt;
