&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The role directly impacts the company&#39;s market, specifically by leading efforts to convert leads into Marketing Qualified Leads (MQLs), and increasing the conversion from MQL to Opportunities Validated and MQL to Launched Won Deals. This role directly impacts pipeline generation, increasing sales opportunities and supporting overall revenue growth across the region.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
